description: Erection of a part 5 and part 6 storey building and a part 4 and part 5 storey building along Enfield Road, a 3-storey terrace along Hertford Road and the conversion of the existing school building to provide 105 dwellings, comprising 23 x 1 bed units, 49 x 2 bed units, 22 x 3 bed units, 3 x 4 bed units,  2 x 4 bed houses and 6 x 5 bed houses, a 215sqm B1/D1 (Office/Community) unit, 39 car parking spaces and the demolition of existing buildings excluding the Victorian former school building.
